Package sandra.examples.formfill.musicbrain

Class Summary
Album Represents a music album
AlbumComparator Custom comparator for Album objects.
MusicBrain MusicBrain: App that engages in a form-filling dialog in which the user provides a word, and a start and end date, and the app shows a list of all music albums in the MusicBrainZ database that contain the word in the title and were released between the dates provided It uses the ASRLib and TTSLib libraries for speech recognition and synthesis, and the FormFillLib for dialog management.
MusicBrainParser Parses a XML file with the response of a release search in MusicBrainZ
 

Exception Summary
MusicBrainException Exception class that allows a more fine-grained management of exceptions providing a possible reason for them that can be communicated to the user
